# ==============================================================================
# Phishing is very frequently used by shipping and postal companies
# The criminals want to obtain addresses and credit card information.
# 
# They use the sender addresses of well-known parcel companies,
# modifying them or adding extra information.
#
# The goal is to create a sense of urgency and make the email appear important.
#
# Real sender names are:
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# DHL Express
# DHL Paket
# DPD Schweiz
# Fedex Tracking
# GLS Paket
# Hermes Benachrichtigungsfunktion
# Hermes Paketankündigung
# Hermes Paketversand
# MyDPD
# Planzer Paket
#
# Die Schweizerische Post
# Post CH AG - Info Sendungsstatus
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Language: german and english
# Weight:   12.0
# ==============================================================================

# Combined
# ==============================================================================

# DHL, DPD, GLS and UPS combinations
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Locations
/(dhl|dpd|fedex|gls|ups).{0,5}(deutschland|germany|korea|swiss)/i
/(dhl|fedex|gls|ups).{0,5}schweiz/i

